channel.title: [REQ] MMO Flappy Bird Logo
channel.description:
Hello,
I am working on a new project for an MMO Flappy Bird - [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,660100.msg4413835.html#new]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,660100.msg4413835.html#new[/url]
I am looking for someone who can make a nice logo for the actual project. What is needed: A Flappy Bird bird On the background of something that will give you the idea that it is Online and Multiplayer. (Can be Network sign, internet sign etc....) This is it..... Be creative :)
Credit will be given for the person who makes the chosen Logo.
Thanks, Twins
